      static class  HwmfPalette.WmfAnimatePalette
      The META_ANIMATEPALETTE record redefines entries in the logical palette that is defined in the playback device context with the specified Palette object The logical palette that is specified by the Palette object in this record is the source of the palette changes, and the logical palette that is currently selected into the playback device context is the destination.(Meta_ANIMATEPALETTE记录用指定的调色板对象重新定义在回放设备上下文中定义的逻辑调色板中的条目。由该记录中的调色板对象指定的逻辑调色板是调色板改变的源，并且当前被选择到回放设备上下文中的逻辑调色板是目的地。)
      static class  HwmfPalette.WmfCreatePalette
      The META_CREATEPALETTE record creates a Palette Object(Meta_CREATEPALETTE记录创建收件箱对象)
      static class  HwmfPalette.WmfPaletteParent 
      static class  HwmfPalette.WmfRealizePalette
      The META_REALIZEPALETTE record maps entries from the logical palette that is defined in the playback device context to the system palette.(Meta_REALIZEPALETTE记录将回放设备上下文中定义的逻辑调色板的条目映射到系统调色板。)
      static class  HwmfPalette.WmfResizePalette
      The META_RESIZEPALETTE record redefines the size of the logical palette that is defined in the playback device context.(Meta_RESIZEPALETTE记录重新定义了播放设备上下文中定义的逻辑调色板的大小。)
      static class  HwmfPalette.WmfSelectPalette
      The META_SELECTPALETTE record defines the current logical palette with a specified Palette Object.(META_SEN CTPALETTE记录用指定的收件箱对象定义当前逻辑调色板。)
      static class  HwmfPalette.WmfSetPaletteEntries
      The META_SETPALENTRIES record defines RGB color values in a range of entries in the logical palette that is defined in the playback device context.(Meta_SETPALENTRIES记录定义在回放设备上下文中定义的逻辑调色板中的条目范围中的RGB颜色值。)
